- "plummeting" is used to describe a rapid and steep fall;
- The percentage drop is calculated as (previous week's points - current week's points) / previous week's points * 100.

- "active players" refers to players whose `player_status` is 'active';
- "total fantasy points scored by the team" is the sum of the fantasy points scored by the players in the team's starting roster;
- "average fantasy points scored by the players in the team" is the average of the fantasy points scored by the players in the team's starting roster.

- "shone the brightest" refers to the highest total fantasy points scored;
- "league" refers to the context of the fantasy sports game;
- "top three players" refers to the players with the highest ranks based on their total fantasy points.

